headline: Marsh McLennan Completes Acquisition of McGriff Insurance Services
summary: NEW YORK, November 15, 2024--Marsh McLennan (NYSE: MMC), a global leader in risk, strategy and people, today completed the acquisition of McGriff Insurance Services, LLC. With the closing of this acquisition, McGriff’s more than 3,500 colleagues will join Marsh McLennan Agency.
